    "The study suggests a need for critical examination of AI-enabled software designed to identify and classify text as either human-written or generated.",
    "Investigating the methods employed in making such distinctions is vital.",
    "Moreover, assessing whether a human can achieve comparable results in discerning the origin and originality of a text would be valuable.",
    "If feasible, this capability could significantly aid educators in efficiently evaluating the authenticity of written content.",
